abstract.text: A configuration object you use to create a tensor.

inlineContent.text: This class contains the mathematical properties of a tensor, such as data type and shape. It also includes initializers that help you create a tensor descriptor for common use cases, such as convolutional neural networks and recurrent neural networks.

abstract.text: Accelerate training and validation of neural networks across the CPU and one or more GPUs.
